usually waived.

118
00:07:43,416 --> 00:07:46,500
With us here, Miharu
should have been fine.

119
00:07:46,583 --> 00:07:48,166
But, even with the two of
you here, they took her.

120
00:07:48,250 --> 00:07:51,041
So, why?

121
00:07:51,125 --> 00:07:55,875
I think I know. It's because
of Miharu's unique ability.

122
00:07:55,958 --> 00:07:58,333
