124
00:08:00,625 --> 00:08:03,208
The same mark your mother has.

125
00:08:03,291 --> 00:08:06,750
Well, uh... yes.

126
00:08:06,833 --> 00:08:09,125
So that mark... it's like...

127
00:08:09,208 --> 00:08:10,750
Sacred.

128
00:08:10,833 --> 00:08:12,416
It... is?

129
00:08:12,500 --> 00:08:13,708
That's right.

130
00:08:13,791 --> 00:08:15,375
They call it the star mark.

131
00:08:15,458 --> 00:08:18,083
You see, whosoever
wears the star mark

132
00:08:18,166 --> 00:08:20,083
has the power to open
a watery gateway

133
00:08:20,166 --> 00:08:22,833
between Seiren and Earth.

134
00:08:22,916 --> 00:08:26,333
Anyone who's born with that
mark can open a gateway.

135
00:08:26,416 --> 00:08:27,416
It's rare.

136
00:08:27,500 --> 00:08:29,083
