139
00:08:33,958 --> 00:08:35,083
Chief Nanae and myself
are the only ones

140
00:08:35,166 --> 00:08:38,458
in our department
who know about this.

141
00:08:38,541 --> 00:08:41,125
The only reason
I've known about it

142
00:08:41,208 --> 00:08:44,083
is because my mother had
the same sacred mark.

143
00:08:44,166 --> 00:08:47,125
My father was brought to Seiren
through my mother's power,

144
00:08:47,208 --> 00:08:50,791
just like Miharu
brought Yukinari.

145
00:08:50,875 --> 00:08:52,166
but...

146
00:08:52,250 --> 00:08:53,583
The Special Forces.

147
00:08:53,666 --> 00:08:55,166
Yes.

148
00:08:55,250 --> 00:08:58,125
But why would they kidnap a girl
being watched by bureau agents?

149
00:08:58,208 --> 00:09:00,208
I have no idea.

150
00:09:00,291 --> 00:09:01,916
But if they went to the trouble

151
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:03,000
of sending an agent
all the way to Earth,

152
00:09:03,083 --> 00:09:07,750
and keeping her
so deep under cover...

153
00:09:07,833 --> 00:09:10,291
