154
00:09:10,375 --> 00:09:12,333
The gateway that connects us
between Seiren and Earth

155
00:09:12,416 --> 00:09:15,791
has already been sealed.

156
00:09:15,875 --> 00:09:17,375
And without our Aqua Lamps,

157
00:09:17,458 --> 00:09:21,166
we can't even send them a
transmission to ask why.

158
00:09:21,250 --> 00:09:23,333
